dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Michael Henderson. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Patricia. Let's start by confirming your date of birth, if you don't mind. Could you please spell out the month and day?
Great, thank you. And can you provide the last four digits of your driver's license number for verification purposes?
Of course. Zero one two four.
Thank you, Patricia. We have successfully verified your information. Do you have any specific inquiries or requests regarding your auto insurance policy today?
I wanted to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
I can assist you with that. Please provide me with the make, model, and year of the vehicle you wish to add.
It's a Toyota Camry, two zero one nine.
Thank you for the information, Patricia. I will update your policy accordingly. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
Thank you for your time, Patricia. Have a wonderful day.
